<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/html-head', {title: ""}); -%>

<body>
  <div id="app" class="wrap">
    <header>
      <%- include('partials/nav'); -%>
      <h1 class="page-title"><em>Veenew</em> - <span style="font-weight: normal;">Your corner of the web</span></h1>
    </header>

    <section>
      <p>Veenew (pronounced as venue) is a simple microblogging platform at its core, but flexible enough for blogs, essays, journals, personal website, and everything in between.</p>
      <p>Built on open standards with ActivityPub & RSS support, so your blog connects seamlessly with the Fediverse. It brings the freedom of traditional blogging to microblogging - a clean space to write, share, and connect on your terms. No follows, no likes, just your thoughts.</p>

      <a href="/signup"><button>get started for free</button></a>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
    </section>
    <section id="features">
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3>Pure Writing, Zero Distractions</h3>
          No likes, no comments, no follower counts. Just you and your words. Focus on what matters without the anxiety of social metrics or endless notifications.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Instant Setup</h3>
          Get your <code>username.veenew.com</code> subdomain and start posting in seconds. No complex configuration, no technical knowledge required. Sign up, choose your username, and you're live.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Make It Yours</h3>
          Customize with your own CSS to match your style, or upgrade to connect your personal domain. Full control over your blog's look and feel, from minimal typography to bold custom designs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Fediverse-Ready</h3>
          Built-in ActivityPub support. Your profile lives on the open web and can be followed from Mastodon, Pixelfed, and other federated platforms. Join the decentralized social web without leaving your own space.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Markdown Everything</h3>
          Write with formatting, embed images and videos, create unlimited custom pages with clean URLs. Full Markdown support means you can structure posts exactly how you want, with headers, lists, code blocks, and media.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Always Ad-Free</h3>
          No ads. Not now, not ever. Your space stays yours. We don't sell your attention, track your readers, or clutter your writing with promotional content.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>RSS Built-In</h3>
          Every profile gets an RSS feed automatically - let readers follow their way. Whether they use Feedly, NewsBlur, or any RSS reader, your content is accessible beyond the web browser.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>True Data Ownership</h3>
          Export all your content anytime. No lock-in, no questions asked. Your words belong to you, and you can take them anywhere, whenever you want.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>No Artificial Limits</h3>
          Microblog thoughts, publish long-form essays, or mix both. Write what you want, when you want. There's no character count, no post frequency restrictions, no algorithm deciding what deserves attention.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <a href="/signup"><button>get started</button></a>

    </section>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <section id="pricing">
      <h2>Pricing</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Free forever for everyone.</strong> Write, publish, and share without ever paying a cent.
        All core features included - no trials, no limits, no catches.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Upgrade only if you need it.</strong> Want to use your own domain or embed analytics scripts?
        One-time payment of <strong>$36</strong>. Pay once, enjoy forever. No subscriptions, no recurring fees.
      </p>
    </section>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <section>

      <blockquote><em>Just a calm corner of the internet where you can write and share on your own terms.</em></blockquote>
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <p>Curious how it looks? View a sample profile: <a href="https://vasanth.veenew.com">vasanth.veenew.com</a></p>
    </section>

    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <%- include('partials/footer'); -%>
  </div>
</body>

</html>